ON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3491\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3491-TW</a>)、華通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>♦PCB 敬鵬 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2355:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2355\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2355-TW</a>)、散熱奇鋐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>)、雷射鑽孔機達航科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:4577:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4577\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4577-TW</a>)、被動禾伸堂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3026:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3026\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3026-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>※策略：急漲不追，惟遇拉回量縮，只要守穩 10 日線或關鍵支撐不破，逢低仍是值得留意，尤其是<strong> CPO</strong><strong> 光通訊／</strong><strong>CoWoS</strong><strong> 先進封裝與設備／低軌衛星</strong><strong> (</strong><strong>LEO</strong><strong>)</strong><strong> 等</strong><strong>，長期爆發成長潛力強勁，更是值得留意</strong><strong>。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</sectio